---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Resume"
  description="Professional background with 25+ years in technology, specializing in Agile, DevOps, and servant leadership. Application Architect and technical leader."
>
  <div class="page resume-page">
    <h1 class="page-title">Resume</h1>

    <section class="resume-content">
      <p>
        <strong>Current Status:</strong> Not seeking new roles; focusing full-time on book writing as
        of May 2025.
      </p>

      <h2>Professional Overview</h2>
      <p>
        A collaborative leader with 25+ years in technology, specializing in the intersection of
        "people, process, and technology" with expertise in Agile, DevOps, and servant leadership.
      </p>

      <h2>Recent Experience</h2>

      <h3>MassMutual (2019-2025)</h3>

      <h4>Application Architect (2022-2025)</h4>
      <p>
        Led governance and observability initiatives, managing cloud migrations and developer
        communities.
      </p>

      <h4>Technical Lead (2020-2022)</h4>
      <p>Oversaw customer portal development from concept through production.</p>

      <h4>Full Stack Developer (2019-2020)</h4>
      <p>Built applications in React, Node.js, and TypeScript.</p>

      <h3>Earlier Career</h3>

      <h4>MEDITECH (2003-2019)</h4>
      <p>
        Progressed from technical support through various development roles to lead programmer, with
        emphasis on Agile transition, code review, and process improvement.
      </p>

      <h4>RCN (1996-2001)</h4>
      <p>Network engineering and technical support roles.</p>

      <h2>Education</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Master's in Software Development - Boston University</li>
        <li>PMI Agile Certified Practitioner</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Speaking</h2>
      <p>
        Has presented on leading organizational change and technical troubleshooting at industry
        conferences and professional organizations, including LeadDev StaffPlus and Enterprise
        Technology Leadership Summit.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .resume-content {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .resume-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }

  .resume-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }

  .resume-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }

  .resume-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .resume-content ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .resume-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .resume-content strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
  }
</style>
